infoparam.name: UML Note
infoparam.value:
- Serve hot drink to the user.
- Provide the user the choice between tea or coffee.
- Proceed the payment for the bevarage using coins.
- Notify the user when the drink is ready.
- Use only the user's personal mug.
- Notify the user in case of missing resources.

Line.value: - Serve hot drink to the user.
- Provide the user the choice between tea or coffee.
- Proceed the payment for the bevarage using coins.
- Notify the user when the drink is ready.
- Use only the user's personal mug.
- Notify the user in case of missing resources.

textline.data: Preparation time
- between 5 and 6 seconds for coffee
- between 6 and 7 seconds for tea

infoparam.name: UML Note
infoparam.value: The system to be designed is the controller of the coffee machine, not the entire machine

Line.value: The system to be designed is the controller of the coffee machine, not the entire machine

textline.data: The bell shall ring during 2 seconds.
The controller shall keep the customer informed.
The system shall handle coffee
and tea preparation and delivery.
A coin slot shall accept 50 cents coins exclusively.
The cost for one coffee is 50 cents.
The controller shall be triggered by the device
in charge of accepting payments.
The system shall dispense one coffee against one payment by the customer.
The controller shall manage
a drink preparation device.
The controller shall be connected
to a drink selection device.
The controller shall monitor a display device.
The controller shall ring a bell.
The controller shall start the preparation process
after completion of payment and drink selection.
The controller shall handle drink delivery
when the drink is ready.
The controller shall handle water, sugar, coffee,
teau, and cups whilst preparing a drink.
The controller will never suffer a power cut.
The shut down of the controller is not modeled.
Neither scheduled nor upon request maintenance are modeled.
The set up of the controller is not modeled.
Not modeled.
Assumption description:
Double-click to edit
Assumption description:
Double-click to edit
The controller will never fail.
All the input and output devices will be permanently connected to the controller..
None of the controller's input and output devices will ever fail.

infoparam.name: UML Note
infoparam.value: For tea : replace selectCoffee by selectTea and replace prepareCoffee by prepareTea.

Line.value: For tea : replace selectCoffee by selectTea
